    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "# LMHG Louisville SEO and AI Visibility Dashboard\nDataForSEO baseline for Louisville Mental Health Group. The run stayed far under budget and exposes three urgent themes: crawler access, AI citation gaps, and head-term/local-grid ranking work.",
        "id": "block-01"
      },
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "**Baseline KPIs:** spend `$4.281544`; LLM mentions `11/48`; LLM citations `8/48`; Google AI Mode citations `0/17`; DataForSEO OnPage crawled `0` pages because of `forbidden_http_header`; Google Business Profile has `19` reviews at `4.4` average.",
        "id": "block-02"
      },
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "## Spend and API Mix\nThe run used a broad but tightly scoped mix of SERP, Labs, AI Optimization, Business Data, Backlinks, and OnPage endpoints.",
        "id": "block-03"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-04",
        "chartId": "chart-cost"
      },
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "## AI and Agentic Search Visibility\nDirect LLM responses occasionally found LMHG, but Google AI Mode did not cite the site for tested Louisville prompts. These charts and tables show where copy and FAQ answers need to be made more citable.",
        "id": "block-05"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-06",
        "chartId": "chart-llm-platform"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-07",
        "chartId": "chart-ai-mode"
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "id": "block-08",
        "tableId": "table-ai-mode"
      },
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "## Louisville Ranking Priorities\nThe highest-volume terms are therapy, therapist, and counseling Louisville KY. Case management is the clear current strength; child, family, in-home, and community-based services need stronger local and answer-engine signals.",
        "id": "block-09"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-10",
        "chartId": "chart-keywords"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-11",
        "chartId": "chart-local-grid"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-12",
        "chartId": "chart-depth"
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "id": "block-13",
        "tableId": "table-local-grid"
      },
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "## Competitors and Off-Page Signals\nKentucky Counseling Center, UofL Health, Seven Counties, LifeStance, Best Life, and other local providers repeatedly appear in SERP and LLM citation surfaces. Backlink cleanup is also required because DataForSEO sees many broken backlink targets.",
        "id": "block-14"
      },
      {
        "type": "chart",
        "id": "block-15",
        "chartId": "chart-competitors"
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "id": "block-16",
        "tableId": "table-competitors"
      },
      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "body": "## Implementation Backlog\nThe backlog is ordered for impact: make the site crawlable to SEO tooling, fix soft-404 behavior, then improve entity copy/schema/FAQ surfaces for local and agentic queries.",
        "id": "block-17"
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "id": "block-18",
        "tableId": "table-actions"
      }
    ]
  },
